# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, if you're executing network checks, it can be useful to ignore it.
#Lockfile should be committed.

# poetry
#   Poetry uses poetry.lock, which should be committed.

# pdm
#   PDM uses pdm.lock, which should be committed.
#   But __pypackages__ is ignored by PEP 582 section above.

# Hatch
.hatch/
